import http.client
import json

conn = http.client.HTTPSConnection("api.kkyyxx.xyz")
payload = json.dumps({
   "quota": 100000,
   "count": 1,
   "expired_time": 0,
   "name": "Test",
   "key": "dwidjuohfuohsdjf"
})
headers = {
   'New-Api-User': '1',
   'Cookie': '-BDC23V7Os3SiI7hng==;-BDC23V7Os3SiI7hng==',
   'new-api-user': '1',
   'Content-Type': 'application/json'
}
conn.request("POST", "/api/redemption/", payload, headers)
res = conn.getresponse()
data = res.read()
print(data.decode("utf-8"))
